        "content": "<p> <strong>We accept the following credit cards:</strong></p><ul><li>American Express</li><li>Discover</li><li>Mastercard</li><li>Visa</li><li>Diners Club</li><li>Apple Pay</li><li>Google Pay</li><li>Facebook Pay</li><li>Shop Pay</li><li>JCB</li><li>Elo</li></ul><p>Once you select checkout, you will be transferred to our secure payment gateway; where you will be able to American Express, Mastercard, Visa, Discover, Diners Club, Apple Pay, Google Pay, Facebook Pay, Shop Pay, JCB, Elo.</p><p><strong>PayPal is not accepted at this moment.</strong></p><p>You can also place your order and pay later with our free-interest installments via ShopPay by Affirm. <br/><br/>Rates from 0%-36% APR. Payment options through Shop Pay Installments, are subject to an eligibility check and are provided by these lending partners: <a href=\"http://affirm.com/lenders\" title=\"http://affirm.com/lenders\">affirm.com/lenders</a>. Options depend on your purchase amount, and a down payment may be required. State notices to consumers <a href=\"https://www.affirm.com/licenses\" title=\"https://www.affirm.com/licenses\">https://www.affirm.com/licenses</a>.\"<br/></p><p><strong>Questions:</strong></p><p>Email: info@shopcarbinox.com</p><p>Monday – Friday: 9:00 AM- 6:00 PM (EST)<br/></p>",
